The paper proposes modifications to a neural network model, specifically the Progressive Operational Perceptron (POP), to improve its learning capability. This suggests that the paper belongs to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with machine learning algorithms and data representations, which are relevant to the Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The proposed modifications also involve image processing, which falls under the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of the modified POP for control systems, which is related to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
